long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A simple to do list extension helps keep track of tasks you need to complete, or things that you want to do. 

This extension helps organise in order of priority. Had enough of traditional paper and pen to do lists, with this extension your able to create new task, add links, set tasks to complete and delete them to. So keeping your tasks up to date couldn't be any easier.
